title: 130: The Snack Haul Episode (January ’21 Edition)
itunes:title: The Snack Haul Episode (January ’21 Edition)
description: Tune in as Lisa, Jamie, and Mikey taste-test a wide array of snacks: freeze-dried lychee, freeze-dried avocado, a crunchy chocolate treat, a 10-calorie cauliflower snack, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, a sprouted almond snack that you have to order RIGHT NOW! No time to wait… Push play, and then head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of the products mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: It’s time to SNACK with Hungry Girl on this week’s episode of Chew the Right Thing!
